{"tid":466730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莊士倫敦廣場連續兩個周五晚停電　邊爐客摸黑離場","createTime":"2017-11-12T23:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T09:51:14.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e416f127eb04cd3320c565c05797e57f814ae318","tid":466730,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/132646/thumbnail/ed0eea0b47412e4e22640bde0243e4b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F132646%2Fthumbnail%2Fed0eea0b47412e4e22640bde0243e4b8.jpg&h=c23b9d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佐敦莊士倫敦廣場昨晚（10日）又停電！該大廈短短一周已第二度停電，3至13樓食肆於8時許晚市黃金時段再「熄燈」。食客無所適從，據知電力短時間內無法恢復，部分食客唯有離開，商戶一周內又再蒙受損失。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/971797/xlarge/542dac2752d15f537f89854ebf2677c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F971797%2Fxlarge%2F542dac2752d15f537f89854ebf2677c4.jpg&h=db7750d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨晚停電時，食肆內烏燈黑火。（網民Chung On Leung攝）<br />\n<br />\n昨（10日）晚上8時許，有網民指莊士倫敦廣場一所食肆用饍時，大廈3至13樓又再停電，現場伸手不見五指，食客在黑暗之中等待。該網民指，管理處短時間內不能維修電力運作，於是食店內客人陸續摸黑離場，但近9時左右，食肆又短暫回復電力，直至9時15分電力供應才回復正常。但網民指，當時食肆全場只剩下5、6台客人。該網民稱，剛剛入座不久的食客無須付款即可離開，但用饍已久則仍須埋單找數。<br />\n<br />\n上周五（3日），莊士倫敦廣場７時許疑因電錶房故障突然停電，直至凌晨時份才恢復供電，該日3至13樓食肆全晚停止營業，大量食客摸黑沿樓梯返回地面。不少食肆商戶損失營業額、叫苦連天，豈知一周內再次停電。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/971798/xlarge/9c7aaa34b67aef3377c07873b3e1f85d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F971798%2Fxlarge%2F9c7aaa34b67aef3377c07873b3e1f85d.jpg&h=6efb0ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漆黑中，只見食客手機熒幕光芒。（網民Chung On Leung攝）<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇？<br />\n短期停兩次　應該座樓供電好可能有問題－網民Pak Wong<br />\n逢星期五就停電－網民L Sam Sam<br />\n結婚擺酒就大鑊－網民Christopher Wong<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/132646/-%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E5%81%9C%E9%9B%BB-%E8%8E%8A%E5%A3%AB%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E6%99%9A%E5%81%9C%E9%9B%BB-%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%E5%AE%A2%E6%91%B8%E9%BB%91%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F132646%2F-%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%259B%25BB-%25E8%258E%258A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2599%259A%25E5%2581%259C%25E9%259B%25BB-%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%2588%2590%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2591%25B8%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=ToY5HEM1M9s7pBlllVuXYtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0a58f6f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/132646/-%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E5%81%9C%E9%9B%BB-%E8%8E%8A%E5%A3%AB%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E6%99%9A%E5%81%9C%E9%9B%BB-%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%E5%AE%A2%E6%91%B8%E9%BB%91%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4</a>"},{"pid":"bf7e14c17ea4e4c17212dfdd4127df1b915130b1","tid":466730,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f846f96ff47b5dbaff3929dbaeb9fd3842c6e01","tid":466730,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定有人趁機渣波</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e0a0e04e26b51fc3a37dc52964830099461565","tid":466730,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:08:52.000Z","msg":"近唔近佐敦薈?"},{"pid":"cd63291b666362a39100bd3278e01456bdff63f8","tid":466730,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近唔近佐敦薈?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n近嘉利大廈"},{"pid":"d20c648001e33d8f71b89fce21883c6f43bb9836","tid":466730,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"